data.description: Welcome to this stunning home which boasts an exquisite interior and maintenance-free exterior uniquely built in 2022 by L & R Home Designs, LLC. The home includes wood flooring, stunning countertops, and sleek cabinets in the kitchen and bathroom. You'll love the modern look and feel of the space, as well as the added functionality that comes with these updates. In addition to the indoor updates, the home also boasts an extended patio, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the beautiful outdoor surroundings. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere that immediately makes you feel at home. The spacious living room is perfect for spending quality time with loved ones or entertaining guests. The large windows allow natural light to flood the space, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. You'll enjoy preparing meals for your family and friends in this space. The bedrooms are comfortable with plenty of room for relaxation and rest. The home is in short distance of the AT&T Center, Freeman Coliseum, downtown amenities, restaurants, shops, and entertainment. 10yr warranty.
